<div class="author-hero">
    <div>
        <span class="badge bg-light text-dark mb-2">Author of the Week</span>
        <h2>Jane Doe</h2>
        <p class="mb-4" style="max-width: 600px; opacity: 0.9;">
            Celebrated for her innovative approach to modern sci-fi, Jane has captivated readers worldwide with her latest series "The Void Walker".
        </p>
        <button class="btn btn-light text-primary fw-bold px-4 py-2">View Profile</button>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row mb-5">
    <div class="col-12">
        <h3 class="section-title">
